{
  "stem": "753.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they would get in a document, now, go to Rome and pick up those Jews, they would say, we didn't find them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's how the Italian people behaved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now these people where we lived, they were religious Catholics.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were the most altruistic people that you can find in the world.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Imagine that we totally changed their everyday life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is not somebody who came just and gave donation to save those Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to change every minute of their life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They did not have water-- running water, no electricity.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had to carry water from some high well on the top of the mountain.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here we are three more people to carry for them the, the water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we couldn't help them because we were not to be seen outdoors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Could you ever go out of their house?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did-- outdoor a little bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we, [SIGHS] we didn't dare.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If somebody walks by, there were neighbors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They, they to church on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they knew-- they had friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they eliminated their social life totally.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, what these people did for me, I, I wouldn't like to be through-- put to such a test.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I remember, recall, that they found another home for us for a very short time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have very little recollection of this home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We stayed there a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then they couldn't keep us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They found another-- they never let us go-- 'just go and find a place.' They found another home for us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So here we came now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Here we now are on top of the mountain-- a big family, many brothers, many wives.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
